    "description": "Expanded outlier universe for measuring DCF model recalibration impact AND peer-cap firing on mid-cap pharma / IT services / FMCG names. v1 (canary_outliers_7.json) was the launch-day audit snapshot — 7 tickers across mixed sectors. v2 adds ~20 mid-cap names where peer-cap is expected to be the binding constraint, so a regression in the peer-cap path (PR #136) is caught here before it shows up on the public stock pages. Keep canary_stocks_50.json untouched — that is the immutable regression baseline. canary_outliers_v2.json is the *drift* universe.",
