      "revenue_cagr_3y": "3y revenue CAGR (decimal)"
    },
    "rule": "null bound = harness skips that assertion for that stock. Bounds are intentionally wide — the value of this file is in DRIFT measurement (snapshot vs branch) AND in peer-cap-firing assertions, not strict gate assertions.",
