    "v2_additions_2026_04_28": "Added 20 mid-cap names across pharma (8), IT services (6), FMCG (6) where peer-cap should be the binding constraint. If peer-cap fails to fire on any of these, regression on PR #136 (peer-multiple FV ceiling) is the most likely cause."
